Text: How can I seed, the computer is on all the day and transmisson open too.

Using Transmission for OSX, Highlight your uploaded torrent from the main window, go to view menu, select 'show Inspector'. In this window, click the options tab, then under the 'seeding menu' select seed forever from the drop-down menu.

Hope this helps
